; XC Scoreboard Clock Script  
; Send running time to TCP port 5556 in JSON format
; Save to C:\Lynx\ and select in FinishLynx Scoreboard Options
;
; Configuration in FinishLynx:
; - Script: xc-scoreboard-clock.lss
; - Serial Port: Network (UDP) or Network (Connect)
; - IP Address: 127.0.0.1 (or your server IP)
; - Port: 5556
; - Running Time: On
; - Results: Off (clock only, no results on this port)

;;Initialization
; Empty

;;TimeRunning
; Send clock time ~10x per second as JSON
; Format: {"t":"time","c":"update"}
\00{"t":"\01%s","c":"update"}\0a

;;TimeGun
; Send when gun fires
\00{"t":"\01%s","c":"start"}\0a

;;TimeStopped
; Send when timing stops
\00{"t":"\01%s","c":"stop"}\0a

;;TimeUpdate
; Send on timing updates
\00{"t":"\01%s","c":"update"}\0a
